author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: P.S: I’m a broke Luvity, but I do try. Once you guys go on your tour, you bet I’m going to see you guys~!! Take care of yourselves, please~!! It’s not safe just caring for others, you’re human beings as well. And I couldn’t be more thankful for this boy group being formed.

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: you. I just want to say how grateful I am that Cravity has been created. I wouldn’t be where I am if I didn’t support these nine amazingly talented boys. My love towards you is eternal, it wouldn’t end for anything. I’m glad you’re by my side as I am by yours. I love you all~!!💟

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Me. Honestly, I gave up during quarantine. But, I noticed a new bg under starship was debuting, so I knew I was in for a treat. And wow, was I surprised. The vocals, raps, visuals, choreography. Everything drew me towards you. I was so much happier and brighter after discovering-

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Ahn Seongmin. Truly the one who is in for a ride. Your growth every single comeback is always noticeable. You’re growing much more confident and comfortable, and I just love who you’ve became. Your sweet, higher pitched vocals. Your emotion and love with the members. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Kim Taeyoung. My Youngtae~!! The man that you’re growing into should be so proud of himself. You’re the mood maker, always laughing with people. Always trying to make them laugh in some way or another. Your dedication towards performing, always giving it your all. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Song Hyeongjun. Stole my heart since day one, and has kept it ever since. The growth I’ve witnessed from you brings tears to my eyes. Your confidence, your love and sympathy towards everyone. Your determination to get the dance and vocals right. You make me so proud. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Kang Minhee. May I just say how extremely proud I am of you. Your voice honestly feels like a warm hug. So comforting and reassuring to the ears and heart. Visual introvert of the group, definitely. The shy but bold man that you are, Mini. Keep striving forward. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Ham Wonjin. An inspiration to many. Such an amazing performer who gets lost in the music every time. The time and dedication you put into everything is unbelievable. Your voice, your dance style, your cute goofy tactics are just the cutest. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Seo Woobin. When I say talent at it’s finest, I’m describing him. His love and dedication towards music in general is so inspiring. Having one of the most warmest and safest voice I’ve ever heard in my life. The comfort you bring to me and your members is so loving. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Koo Jungmo. An exceptional performer. A total flirt with all the members. Such a big heart. An amazing voice with as amazing control. The visuals are just indescribable. Always so loving towards the other 8 members and Luvity as well~!! I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Allen Ma. An amazing representative for Californians. Definitely an all-rounder. Just from the first performance I’ve seen from you, I knew you would shine all throughout. Your hard energized raps, your encouraging spirit towards the members is so sweet of you. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Park Serim. You’re such an amazingly caring leader. Always there for the members no matter the problem or situation. And may I say such a charismatic rapper and performer. From that to the most purest soul ever in existence. You have such a kind and loving heart. I love you~!

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: They always interact with their fans as much as possible. Giving us hope in everything, and I really appreciate them for always being positive. They keep their promises and fulfill them to a higher standards every time. Their bond is so heartwarming, they really are a family.

author: ♡ Luvisé ♡ CALI BOI LENI DAY ♡
text: Wow, happy anniversary to Cravity. Can’t believe they debuted 2 years ago. It honestly feels like they were announced to debut a minute ago. The growth I’ve witnessed from all nine of them makes me so proud. From their debut, to their most recent comeback. CRAVITY doesn’t fail.-
